data.description: This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 and a half bathroom house is situated near Lake Ray Hubbard and is just a short distance from shopping and dining. You will be greeted by luxurious upgrades throughout. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with gorgeous walnut butcher block countertops. In the main living area, you'll find a custom bar, stunning chandelier, and a double-sided fireplace that leads into a secondary living space. The venetian plaster walls add a special touch to the home. The master bedroom, located on the first floor, offers a private retreat. Head up the beautiful staircase to find the additional bedrooms, a loft, and an outdoor patio. During the winter months, you can enjoy your morning coffee while taking in the serene lake views. Your backyard oasis is complete with a pool and an outdoor kitchen. Don't forget about the bonus room perfect for a man cave with a pool table and mini fridge already set up for your enjoyment. Motivated Seller bring your offers!
